<p class="lead">
Commissioning this review of health and social care is the most important act of my time as Health Minister to date. Following through with it will be my priority for the rest of my tenure.
</p>
<!-- RW: 34248856 k: reference-default-34248856-sec-opinion_newsanalysis-art e: 20m d: -->
<div class="widget ad google" >
<script async src="//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script>
<ins class="adsbygoogle"
style="display:inline-block;width:620px;height:90px"
data-ad-client="ca-pub-1729148518344007"
data-ad-slot="1876002781"
data-max-num-ads = "2"></ins>
<script>
(adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
</script>
</div>
<p>Our health service is vital to everyone in Northern Ireland. We in the Executive and in the Assembly, as leaders, are duty-bound to protect and enhance this service.</p>
<div class="w w115" data-widget="Redesign Article Page tools Widget Persistent">
